query:
/*+  */ select dd.d_year,
i.i_brand_id AS brand_id,
i.i_brand AS brand,
sum(ss.ss_ext_sales_price) AS sum_agg
from item AS i
inner join store_sales AS ss
on ss.ss_item_sk = i.i_item_sk AND i.i_manufact_id = 977
inner join date_dim AS dd
on dd.d_date_sk = ss.ss_sold_date_sk AND dd.d_moy = 12 group by dd.d_year, i.i_brand, i.i_brand_id order by dd.d_year, sum_agg desc, brand_id LIMIT 100;
